h could adversely impact their financial stability in the long run.\n\n## O Analyst Forecast & Price Prediction\n\n## Start investing in O\n\nOrder type\n\nBuy in\n\nOrder amount\n\nEst. shares\n\n0 shares", 'score': 0.9998118, 'raw_content': None}, {'url': 'https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/O/', 'title': 'Realty Income Corporation (O) Stock Price, News, Quote & History', 'content': "FY25\n\nQ2\n\nFY25\n\nQ3\n\nFY25\n\nQ4\n\nFY25\n\n0\n\n500M\n\n1B\n\nView More\n\n### Analyst Insights: O\n\nView More \n\n### Analyst Price Targets\n\n60.00\n\n67.85 Average\n\n60.95 Current\n\n75.00 High\n\n### Analyst Recommendations\n\n### Latest Rating\n\nDate 3/17/2026\n\nAnalyst Evercore ISI Group\n\nRating Action Maintains\n\nRating In-Line\n\nPrice Action Raises\n\nPrice Target 65 -> 67\n\nView More\n\n### Statistics: O\n\nView More \n\n### Valuation Measures\n\nAs of 3/20/2026\n\n Market Cap\n\n  56.83B\n Enterprise Value\n\n  85.74B\n Trailing P/E\n\n  52.09\n Forward P/E\n\n  38.02\n PEG Ratio (5yr expected)\n\n  --\n Price/Sales (ttm)\n\n  9.63\n Price/Book (mrq)\n\n  1.44\n Enterprise Value/Revenue\n\n  14.91\n Enterprise Value/EBITDA\n\n  17.92\n\n### Financial Highlights\n\n#### Profitability and Income Statement\n\n Profit Margin\n\n  18.37%\n Return on Assets (ttm) [...] Realty Income Corporation, an S&P 500 company, is real estate partner to the world's leading companies. We serve our clients as a full-service real estate capital provider. As of December 31, 2025, we have a portfolio of over 15,500 properties in all 50 states of the United States (U.S.), the United Kingdom (U.K.), and eight other countries in Europe. We are known as (The Monthly Dividend Company) and have a mission to invest in people and places to deliver dependable monthly dividends that increase over time. Since our listing on the NYSE in 1994, we have had 133 dividend increases and are a member of the S&P 500 Dividend Aristocrats index for having increased our dividend for over 31 consecutive years.